{"tid":1657012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"poly新橋開幕，大家係咪有樣野唔記得咗？","createTime":"2019-10-16T01:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T01:20:53.000Z","uid":188582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c04ba35993b4b70feba224a537a7a402be06b18","tid":1657012,"uid":188582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190907/bkn-20190907201219046-0907_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190907%2Fbkn-20190907201219046-0907_00822_001.html&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVgg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=55e706a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190907/bkn-20190907201219046-0907_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今日(7日)晚上7時許，1名31歲姓鍾男子，被發現倒臥於紅磡理工大學Z座地下，頭部受傷昏迷不醒，保安員立即報警。救護員接報到場，檢查後證實昏迷男子明顯死亡。警方封鎖現場，經初步調查後，相信鍾從上址墮樓，現場未檢獲遺書，正調查他墮樓原因，並通知其親人到場認屍，案件列作有人從高處墮下。<br />\n理工大學發言人表示，死者不是理大學生。現場消息稱，死者身上有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港專業教育學院學生證</span>及身份證，在Z座11樓墮下，疑先撞及大樹後墮地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又係IVE，會唔會咁啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n千其唔好裝修poly，會嚇親啲NDS㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f3074cb353023d291c435e537779c540145f00","tid":1657012,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8cbda16ef483f5d36a71d2f966f3d6b9af9345cb","tid":1657012,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:20:53.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n辛苦製作，求手足幫推！！！"}]}